requirement:
Build a simple REST API for Todo Management with the following features:
1. User authentication (JWT)
2. CRUD operations for todos (create, read, update, delete)
3. Todo fields: id, title, description, status, priority, due_date
4. Filter and search capabilities
5. SQLite database
6. Python FastAPI framework
7. Basic unit tests
8. API documentation (OpenAPI/Swagger)
